  "texts": [
    "These methods have refined the process of flavor profiling and have supported the development of food and fragrance products that more effectively reflect consumer preferences.",
    "By applying a range of AI models, including traditional machine learning and deep learning approaches, researchers can now analyze large-scale datasets to identify subtle patterns in taste and aroma.",
    "These capabilities allow for more precise prediction of sensory outcomes, leading to improved product design, enhanced food safety, and the development of consumer-oriented innovations in the flavor and fragrance industries.",
    "This paper also provides a systematic analysis of AI applications in sensory modeling.",
    "It provides a comparative overview of key methods and their use in understanding taste and smell."
